text: Kerenyovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Akhmetovsky Selsoviet, Kushnarenkovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 40 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 25 km from Kushnarenkovo, 7 km from Akhmetovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kushnarenkovsky District
title: Kerenyovo
